data.description: Beautiful home in the highly sought-after Vail School District. Spacious entry way with multi-camera Vivint security system invites you into family room w/surround sound pre-wires, gas fireplace & decorative ceiling fan.  Open kitchen features granite counters, island, SS appliances including brand new refrigerator, plus extended counters w/desk space. There's also an oversized laundry room & specious pantry closet. Backyard showcases Mtn views, flagstone patio, artificial grass & gas fire pit. All bedrooms are upstairs, plus loft & computer niche. Primary Suite includes dual vanities, dual closets, plus separate shower & tub. Security system features smart panel display & includes water, carbon monoxide and fire alarms. Extended driveway and cul-de-sac lot for plenty of guest parking.
